
1. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/1.initialization.yaml 실행

2. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/2.hypercloud4-operator.yaml 실행

3. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/3.secret-watcher.yaml 실행

4. authenticate webhook 설정
    - webhook-config 에 HYPERCLOUD_IP 치환
    - /etc/kubernetes/pki directory 에 webhook-config 복사
	- kube api-server manifest 설정에 아래 문구 추가
	- "--authentication-token-webhook-config-file=/etc/kubernetes/pki/webhook-config"